<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_488_r2l17"><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvildenſtein<ex>er</ex></expan> Als Jr vns <expan>vvıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_488_r2l18"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> brief <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> habt / Darauf ſpricht karl <expan>Holtſchüh<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_488_r2l19"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> . daʒ ew Hanſen <expan>wıldenſtein<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> voraws </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_488_r2l20">vnd auch ſüſt meinklıch doſelbſt vmb vvol wiſſentlıch ſeÿ / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_488_r2l22">die ſchof / 
<del rend="strikethrough">d </del> des Gotſmanns nicht ſein / . ſunder des 
<del rend="strikethrough"> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_488_r2l21"><expan>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> </ab>
