<ab facs="#facs_488_r2l29">vnd ſeins <expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> manns ſein 
<del rend="strikethrough">s </del> / . darnach wir ew darvmb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_488_r2l30">auch <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Nu getrawen vvir ew noch wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_488_r2l31">Jr laſʒet den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd ſeinen <expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> man / an Jren ſchoffen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_488_r2l32">vngeengt / vnd ſagt die <expan>pürge<ex>n</ex></expan> ledig / vnd laſſt vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_488_r2l33">des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> bey <expan>dıſe<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
